    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_6_9742-9830",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9742-9830",
      "markText": "《孙子》只强调进攻，而少谈防御；只强调速胜，而反对持久。这里就无视了被侵略的弱国，必须坚持持久的防御，等待敌军分散、疲惫，然后乘机反击之，这方面的重要性 《孙子》几乎都未谈到。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9742&rangeEnd=9830",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9742&rangeEnd=9830"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_6_10352-10385",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10352-10385",
      "markText": "可是片面强调 “知兵之将”的作用，就不免表现出唯心史观思想的色彩。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10352&rangeEnd=10385",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10352&rangeEnd=10385"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_467-498",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "467-498",
      "markText": "曹操曰：计者，选将、量敌、度地、料卒、远近、险易，计于庙堂也。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=498",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=498"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_5776-5825",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5776-5825",
      "markText": "一个军事家可以自由选择在自己的国内或别国指挥作战，这只是战国时才有的情况。例如吴起在魏，乐毅在燕。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5776&rangeEnd=5825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5776&rangeEnd=5825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_5029-5073",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5029-5073",
      "markText": "一个重要属性，可惜他还未能深入到战争的本质，不能分析不同性质的战争。这是时代和阶级的限制",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5029&rangeEnd=5073",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5029&rangeEnd=5073"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_6915-6979",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6915-6979",
      "markText": "以上四句话通常被称为 “示形”，含有佯动的意思。后来，这些做法被概括为 “声东击西”。总之是用佯动迷惑敌人，以隐蔽我之战略意图。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6915&rangeEnd=6979",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6915&rangeEnd=6979"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_741-789",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "741-789",
      "markText": "孙子曰：兵者，国之大事〔1〕，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。①",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=741&rangeEnd=789",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=741&rangeEnd=789"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_11_1246-1344",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1246-1344",
      "markText": "走迂回的道路，出敌不意由敌人没有配备兵力的地方开进，避免敌之牵制，很快就到达所要争取的战略要地。这样表面看来走的是弯而远的道路，实际上是乘虚而入，能最快通过的 “直”路。这样就是把困难变成有利了。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1344",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1344"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_3972-4071",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3972-4071",
      "markText": "【法者，曲制、官道、主用也】：曲制、官道、主用，据曹注：“曲制者，部曲、旌旗、金鼓之制也。官者，百官之分也。道者，粮路也。主者，主军费用也。”这里讲的是这些制度，规定得适宜不适宜，执行得严格不严格。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3972&rangeEnd=4071",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3972&rangeEnd=4071"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_10_1467-1547",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1467-1547",
      "markText": "《唐太宗李卫公问对》也说：“《孙子》千章万句，无外乎致人而不致于人。”致人而不致于人，就是掌握战场的主动权，也就是军队行动的自由权；这是指导战争的主要原则之一。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1467&rangeEnd=1547",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1467&rangeEnd=1547"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_11_4835-4917",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4835-4917",
      "markText": "（五十三）故其疾如风，（曹操曰：击空虚也。）其徐如林，（曹操曰：不见利也。）侵掠如火，（曹操曰：疾也。）不动如山，（曹操曰：守也。）难知如阴，动如雷震。①",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4835&rangeEnd=4917",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4835&rangeEnd=4917"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_10_1161-1200",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1161-1200",
      "markText": "故善战者，致人而不致于人】：致人，就是调动敌人；不致于人，就是说不被敌人调动。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1161&rangeEnd=1200",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1161&rangeEnd=1200"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_15_11620-11666",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "11620-11666",
      "markText": "此段言简意深，文字优美，实堪三读。“使人无识”和 “若驱群羊”则是剥削阶级军事家难除的糟粕。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=11620&rangeEnd=11666",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=11620&rangeEnd=11666"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_1476-1496",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1476-1496",
      "markText": "一曰道，二曰天，三曰地，四曰将，五曰法。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1476&rangeEnd=1496",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1476&rangeEnd=1496"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_6_9264-9272",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9264-9272",
      "markText": "故兵贵胜，不贵久",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9264&rangeEnd=9272",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9264&rangeEnd=9272"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_17_4128-4152",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "4128-4152",
      "markText": "【非仁义不能使间】：不是仁慈慷慨，不能指使间谍。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4128&rangeEnd=4152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4128&rangeEnd=4152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_5_6370-6405",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6370-6405",
      "markText": "兵者，诡道也。①（曹操曰：兵无常形，以诡诈为道。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6370&rangeEnd=6405",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6370&rangeEnd=6405"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_6_3980-3989",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3980-3989",
      "markText": "取用于国，因粮于敌",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017312&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3980&rangeEnd=3989",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ee32000813ab6d43g0121eb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3980&rangeEnd=3989"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017312_7_842-870",
